These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, sprite
There 2 different types of food: lime, watermelon
The people have 2 different hobbies: collecting, puzzles
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: thriller, martial-arts
1. the person watching thriller movies is not to the right of the person eating watermelon##8
2. the person eating watermelon is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
3. the person drinking lemonade is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | sprite     | lemonade      |
| Food          | watermelon | lime    |
| Hobby         | puzzles   | collecting |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller  | martial-arts      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, lemonade
The people have 2 different hobbies: sudoku, collecting
The people have 2 different jobs:  bartender, accountant
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the left of the bartender##5
3. the accountant is not to the right of the bartender##8
4. the person driving the helicopter is not the person who's hobby is collecting##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | fanta        | lemonade    |
| Hobby       | sudoku         | collecting |
| Job         | accountant | bartender   |
| Transport   | helicopter               | motorbike  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: spy, romance
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: techno, gospel
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, british
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, frog
1. the colombian is in an odd position##4
2. the british is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
3. the fan of techno is somewhere to the left of the person watching romance movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | spy       | romance |
| Music-Genre   | techno       | gospel    |
| Nationality   | colombian | british |
| Pet           | hedgehog        | frog   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-4::.
