2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is not to the left of the person driving the motorbike##8
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Hobby         | card-games | skydiving  |
| Job           | firefighter  | engineer |
| Nationality   | malaysian | argentine   |
| Transport     | motorbike   | helicopter |

