2. the person driving the subway is the person driving the subway##1
3. the person eating garlic is somewhere to the right of the coach##5
4. the person driving the subway is not to the right of the person driving the taxi##8
5. the person driving the taxi is not to the left of the person eating garlic##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |         2          |
